{"id": "1185497060770852914", "channel_id": "1185497060770852914", "type": 0, "author_id": "1069146637416546354", "author_name": "xiaoguopa", "author_bot": false, "content": "过场有一个tips 描述.“融蚀也可以附着在金属等无机物上.”但是无机物的前提是化合物，而金属作为单质似乎归为无机材料更妥当吧", "timestamp": "2023-12-16T08:22:04.758000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1185497060770852914", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「已回答」过场tips 把金属表述为无机物是否不妥？", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960"]}
{"id": "1185415059913064499", "channel_id": "1185415059913064499", "type": 0, "author_id": "559372472177131520", "author_name": "nightglass0424", "author_bot": false, "content": "1.遊戲內的裝備眾多，不論是命輪還是密契都有一個可以契合好幾個角色的時候，不同的場合有不同的用法。\n請問未來有沒有機會，不同隊伍的裝備是可以彼此共用的，像是《緋染天空》不同隊的裝備彼此不干擾；或是有記憶配裝的功能，像是《陰陽師》可以自訂御魂的套裝，一件換上。\n或是讓我在打幕間演習的時候可以不用去拆別人的裝備然後忘記這張原本是誰的…\n\n2.命輪跟密契都有推薦的按鈕，請問推薦的演算是基於那幾個條件去推送的？\n以後可以在角色介面看到大數據的統計嗎？例如其他玩家都裝了那些詞條。", "timestamp": "2023-12-16T02:56:14.230000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "👍", "emoji_id": null, "count": 2}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1185415059913064499", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「已回答」想請問未來能否有這些功能？", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
{"id": "1185444980152606761", "channel_id": "1185444980152606761", "type": 0, "author_id": "662649606131286027", "author_name": "from_far_side", "author_bot": false, "content": "上一场战斗结束最后打了一张绿炎进入超维空间，战斗胜利，但是进入新一场战斗后发现绿炎并未升级，另一张腐化绿炎也没有。\n猜测是战斗胜利结算卡掉了胜利回合的结束升级。", "timestamp": "2023-12-16T04:55:07.771000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1185444980995653682", "filename": "Image_1702702407481.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 2369593, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1185444980152606761/1185444980995653682/Image_1702702407481.png?ex=6a00b86b&is=69ff66eb&hm=edcb8addebdc09ba40ef3dfb8052f033181776d59beb4b31613aac7b34863e7a&"}, {"id": "1185444981708701696", "filename": "Image_1702702268573.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 1184358, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1185444980152606761/1185444981708701696/Image_1702702268573.png?ex=6a00b86c&is=69ff66ec&hm=ef391a969cf9ca38ccb22620a6835295ae644a87c3405ce5e3440d80b54217b7&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1185444980152606761", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「已回答」战斗胜利后超维空间内的绿炎没有升级", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960"]}
